Dialogue: 5,0:01:59.79,0:02:01.74,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I wanna see it too!{overlap}{how the hell does she say "I... too" before the guy even gets past "senpai"}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:02.30,0:02:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember the Boatdrift Ceremony!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:04.66,0:02:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks to that ceremony, happi coats were totally in.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:06.68,0:02:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Happi coats were popular? What the heck?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:09.19,0:02:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu-senpai was so cool!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:11.07,0:02:12.50,Alternative,,0,0,0,,This is too weird.{overlap}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:12.50,0:02:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:13.40,0:02:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Being in the same class as that octopus.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:15.88,0:02:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard that nickname in a while.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.44,0:02:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:19.38,0:02:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, once an octopus, always an octopus.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:21.44,0:02:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like he's changed any.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:23.61,0:02:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but do you guys mind if I sit down{ for a bit}?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:27.11,0:02:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,An old man like me gets tired kinda easily.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:33.51,0:02:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This octopus head over here isn't feeling well just yet,
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.00,0:02:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so you guys shouldn't tease him too much.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:37.80,0:02:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, I haven't heard \Nthat nickname in a while.{yeah, all those 5 years you were sleeping}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:41.69,0:02:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You two had the exact same response.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:43.43,0:02:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, {replace}Senpai, {}aren't you\N technically Shiodome's uncle?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.43,0:02:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So Miuna's your niece?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:49.89,0:02:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but just don't call me "Uncle."
Dialogue: 5,0:02:52.80,0:02:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hikari was his usual self.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:56.25,0:02:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was acting the same\N as he always had before.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:00.03,0:03:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I figured I, too,\N would act like I always had.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:07.83,0:03:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Sensei{Teach}'s voice is all hoarse and raspy now.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't like that before?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:13.84,0:03:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, though I think he used to speak a little faster{ than he does now}.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.85,0:03:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how much have you grown?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:19.94,0:03:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I'm fourt—
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.44,0:03:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Not your age. Your height.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm 158 cm now.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap, you're gonna be taller than me!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.58,0:03:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:29.34,0:03:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. That will definitely not happen.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:32.14,0:03:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But I haven't grown at all \Nin five years, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:36.49,0:03:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do if I'm {now }stuck at this height forever?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:39.94,0:03:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, you can have all my milk.{you'll just have to drink more milk}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.58,0:03:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.01,0:03:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd that guy learn to drive?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.31,0:04:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.88,0:04:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Minegishi!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.19,0:04:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:11.21,0:04:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... about what I told you...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.20,0:04:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. You don't have to say it.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.57,0:04:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:19.92,0:04:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Bu— How did you...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.41,0:04:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't say anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.47,0:04:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank— Sorry...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.29,0:04:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.51,0:04:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's in our class, isn't he?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:41.77,0:04:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep it a secret from your dad for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.88,0:04:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Keep what a secret?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.94,0:04:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You{'ve} gotta tell me one thing, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.84,0:04:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like him, or does \Nhe like you? Which is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:51.20,0:04:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. Forget I asked.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.18,0:04:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand now.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.74,0:04:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand {\i1}what{\i0}?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.38,0:04:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see... So {\i1}that's{\i0} your type.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:59.77,0:05:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:01.10,0:05:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:02.78,0:05:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure. No worries, \NI completely understand.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.30,0:05:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand at all!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:09.57,0:05:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:11.19,0:05:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you started school today.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.07,0:05:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did. I was {replace}quite the senpai{the perfect image \Nof an upperclassman}.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:18.13,0:05:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu-kun brought his old \NMihama Middle School uniform for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,His uniform?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.20,0:05:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't have one.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.32,0:05:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can't very well keep wearing clothes like {\i1}those{\i0} to school.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.88,0:05:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.07,0:05:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\N before the Boatdrift Ceremony,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.58,0:05:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the guys from the fishery cooperative \Ntook my Namiji Middle School uniform.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.47,0:05:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to that one?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:38.00,0:05:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:39.64,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try on this one for now.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.25,0:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If it fits him, feel free to keep it.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:44.87,0:05:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from when I graduated, though,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.88,0:05:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so it might be kinda big on him.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.04,0:05:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.71,0:05:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.00,0:05:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.67,0:05:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.60,0:05:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huge!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.80,0:06:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, Tsumugu grew way too much!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.33,0:06:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I try to take in the pants again?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.72,0:06:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.81,0:06:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.62,0:06:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:11.93,0:06:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just go get you a new uniform.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.24,0:06:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No need for all that.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.18,0:06:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fret about it. \NIt's no trouble.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.10,0:06:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, I can just wear this one.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.83,0:06:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll all take the train, go to the department store, and then eat omelet rice before we come home!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.81,0:06:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Omelet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:35.16,Text on Poisoned Paper,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.05\blur1.5\fscx63\fscy63\pos(205,345)\alpha&H80&\c&H7B7120&\frz14.08}Receipt
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.24,0:06:35.16,Text on Poisoned Paper,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.05\blur0.8\fscx63\fscy63\pos(205,345)\c&H7B7120&\frz14.08}Receipt
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:35.16,Text on Poisoned Paper,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.05\blur1.5\frz17.4\fscx40\fscy40\pos(214,406)\alpha&H80&\c&H7B7120&}Sazanami Pharmacy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.24,0:06:35.16,Text on Poisoned Paper,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.05\blur0.8\frz17.4\fscx40\fscy40\pos(214,406)\c&H7B7120&}Sazanami Pharmacy
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.16,0:06:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They say a boy's bravado is a sign that he's healthy, \Nbut I'm worried about Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.28,0:06:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he {\i1}is{\i0} a guy.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:41.55,0:06:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we let him keep up his façade?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.91,0:06:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.55,0:06:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Itaru-san, thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.00,0:06:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.70,0:06:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For letting Hikari stay at our place.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:53.53,0:06:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to thank me for that.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.82,0:06:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's your little brother.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.55,0:07:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, having such a young brother makes me feel younger myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:04.01,0:07:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Itaru-san...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:05.44,0:07:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's my first day off in a while, \Nso let's all have some fun.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.61,0:07:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for always working so hard.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.58,0:07:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. I should be the one \Nthanking {\i1}you{\i0}, my responsible wife.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.70,0:07:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Omelet...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Omelets are tomorrow.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.13,0:07:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tomorrow"?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.58,0:07:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When's that?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.72,0:07:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When you go beddie-bye and wake up, \Nthat's when tomorrow is.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:42.73,0:07:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.75,0:07:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's special, so let's open another bottle.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.95,0:08:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. We'll have omelets next time, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.68,0:08:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No next time!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.08,0:08:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.32,0:08:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{Whoa!}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.36,0:08:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you bring me a cooling patch for him?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.00,0:08:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. This is for your new uniform.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:21.58,0:08:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. We don't have to go today.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.48,0:08:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.71,0:08:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we don't have to get it made. \NI can just go to Saya Mart and—
Dialogue: 5,0:08:27.86,0:08:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have uniforms there.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.13,0:08:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna, you know where the tailor is, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.96,0:08:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.92,0:08:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.03,0:08:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,See you two later. Be careful.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.03,0:08:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We should get going too.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:46.90,0:08:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a train to catch.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:49.31,0:08:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we just not go?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How come?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.63,0:08:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"How come?"
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.75,0:08:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's not like \NI {\i1}need{\i0} a new uniform.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.22,0:09:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true. Of course you need a proper uniform.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:01.59,0:09:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you're starting to sound just like Akari.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.04,0:09:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:05.20,0:09:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So you keep saying...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:07.90,0:09:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but what'll we do if we get lost?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.26,0:09:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't get lost!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.62,0:09:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}I{\i0} might.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.51,0:09:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll hold hands so we don't get separated.{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.78,0:09:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we going on a date?!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:22.30,0:09:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got that guy from yesterday.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:25.02,0:09:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not—
Dialogue: 5,0:09:25.98,0:09:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right{,} then, I'll invite Sayu to come with us!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:29.38,0:09:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.71,0:09:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go call her. Stay right there.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:44.05,0:09:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bring a bottle of salt water this time?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I didn't!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.43,0:09:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:50.44,0:09:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bring up things from five years ago.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:54.21,0:09:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just the other day for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:56.28,0:09:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, things are different now!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've changed!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.34,0:10:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All right already. Now quit spitting on me.{say it, don't spray it!}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.87,0:10:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not spitting on you!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:05.03,0:10:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.95,0:10:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it that {\i1}you're{\i0} the one who invited me \Nand yet {\i1}I{\i0} had to wait on you?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.42,0:10:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.86,0:10:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:14.59,0:10:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we get for lunch?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.06,0:10:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Omelet rice?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:18.38,0:10:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, I'm not really hungry yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.35,0:10:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember those squid-ink chips we had last time? \NYou know, the black ones.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.77,0:10:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were awesome.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.18,0:10:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they still make 'em?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.16,0:10:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I don't think I've seen them recently.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.24,0:10:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But they have a new flavor: stuffed squid!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuffed squid?! Are you serious?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.66,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds gross.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This place has changed a lot too!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.90,0:10:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.97,0:10:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, have you noticed it kinda smells like something keeps farting?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.94,0:10:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:02.89,0:11:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That was {\i1}not{\i0} a fart!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.02,0:11:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.92,0:11:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's a pig around, then!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:07.78,0:11:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there isn't! That's not it either!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My shoes just keep \Nmaking this weird noise!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.64,0:11:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to her. \NThose are Miuna's best dress shoes.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:14.68,0:11:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your best dress shoes \Nmake pig noises, and fart?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:19.09,0:11:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Farting pig shoes!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:21.45,0:11:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop saying that! They don't fart!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.03,0:11:25.28,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Ow! Quit hitting me! It hurts!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.28,0:11:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, didn't you guys \Nhave something to do?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.16,0:11:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh...}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:28.36,0:11:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,See? We got yelled at.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.87,0:11:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you—
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.82,0:11:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, whatever you say. \NBetter hurry{,} or we'll leave you behind.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.38,0:11:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you remove your shoes \Nand step onto the platform behind you?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.75,0:11:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to take your measurements.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.10,0:11:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:48.69,0:11:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I've made \Na school uniform for someone from the sea.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:52.87,0:11:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll be the first of many more.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.28,0:11:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back with the fabric.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.61,0:12:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I even doing here?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.87,0:12:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Compared to five years ago, there seem to be fewer \Nstudents altogether, including those from the surface.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:12.37,0:12:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I didn't want a Mihama Middle School uniform...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.21,0:12:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}So why are you wearing Mihama's?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:22.80,0:12:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a Mihama Middle School uniform?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.04,0:12:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um, actually...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:26.96,0:12:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,one for Mihama Middle School is fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.62,0:12:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No! He wants one for Namiji Middle School!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.68,0:12:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make it a Namiji Middle School uniform instead!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:33.19,0:12:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Uh...}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.16,0:12:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Namiji Middle School?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that school closed down—
Dialogue: 5,0:12:37.98,0:12:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But he used to go to that school!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.85,0:12:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Please wait here a moment.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.87,0:12:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you—
Dialogue: 5,0:12:47.56,0:12:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Namiji Middle School is fine!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:49.42,0:12:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait outside.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.27,0:13:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you causing the tailor trouble?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:06.37,0:13:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you listening?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:08.36,0:13:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He {told us he }hasn't made a uniform \Nfor someone from the sea in years.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.40,0:13:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.67,0:13:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's whatever.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.89,0:13:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for inviting you on such short notice.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:18.38,0:13:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No big deal.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.83,0:13:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you know?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.16,0:13:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.02,0:13:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,On second thought, I'd better not say it.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.53,0:13:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:26.93,0:13:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't wanna get you mad.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't get mad!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.54,0:13:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.91,0:13:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,did you know a niece can't \Nget married to her uncle?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.86,0:13:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they're close relatives and all.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:39.57,0:13:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.96,0:13:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:43.27,0:13:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't matter, \Nbecause he's your step-uncle.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:47.29,0:13:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I didn't mean to stick my nose in.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.62,0:13:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.82,0:13:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}Forget I said anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:55.42,0:13:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I what?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.88,0:14:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you happy for me?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:01.57,0:14:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you were happy for me, Sayu?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So how could you?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:08.06,0:14:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This and that are completely unrelated.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:10.06,0:14:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're not!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.17,0:14:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being mean, Sayu!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.19,0:14:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the one being mean, Miuna!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.83,0:14:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:17.62,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you invite me to go \Nshopping with you two?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.38,0:14:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've just gone by yourselves!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.02,0:14:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just wanna flaunt \Nyour flirting in my face?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:24.16,0:14:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Flirt"— We're not flirting!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.34,0:14:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You are!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:27.50,0:14:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be nice, huh?!{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:29.40,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The person {\i1}you{\i0} like woke up.{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.95,0:14:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:34.31,0:14:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All the good things always \Nhappen to you, Miuna-chan!{italics you, possibly 277 too}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.68,0:14:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fair!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.81,0:14:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd{bleh} I even come today?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.19,0:14:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I have to make it \Nfrom the Namiji Middle School pattern,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.40,0:14:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it might take a while.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.80,0:14:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,On second thought, never mind.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.98,0:14:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.71,0:14:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need a new uniform after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.68,0:14:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.42,0:14:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.33,0:14:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh...}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:01.57,0:15:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu, you're being a jerk!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.70,0:15:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, {\i1}you're{\i0} the jerk, Miuna!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:08.32,0:15:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.59,0:15:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm going home!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:14.37,0:15:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{Uh...}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.93,0:15:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Shiodome residence.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.57,0:15:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi, Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.11,0:15:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.30,0:15:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he has rubella.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:29.56,0:15:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We got him some medicine, \Nthough, so he'll be fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.04,0:15:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:35.07,0:15:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I got separated from Miuna...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If she called?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.02,0:15:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't heard from her.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.76,0:15:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong? \NShe's not somewhere close to you?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, she's not...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:44.42,0:15:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll start heading back now. See ya soon.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.29,0:15:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.36,0:15:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:57.72,0:16:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to figure out what we should do \Nto kill time till the next train.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.36,0:16:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But we missed it 'cause of me.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:05.13,0:16:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You two haven't changed at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:10.87,0:16:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now! You can't be \Nmaking girls cry like that.
