Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:16.16,Maschinenzimmer.412,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\c&H5F41AF&\b1\fscx75\fscy75\pos(499,554)}Saya           Mart
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayama!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.19,0:16:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that all? You gave this old man \Nquite a scare, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.25,0:16:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You? An old man?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.20,0:16:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit trying to act all mature.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.46,0:16:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:25.66,0:16:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know about all sorts of things now.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.37,0:16:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I take it back. You {\i1}are{\i0} a geezer.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.72,0:16:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So since the store isn't as busy as it used to be,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:43.74,0:16:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we went back to selling stuff door-to-door.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.77,0:16:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, this shipyard we're passing...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:49.56,0:16:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,About three or four years ago, there were talks about demolishing it and putting up a parking lot.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:53.64,0:16:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But who'd even use it, right?{Not like anyone would use it, though.}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the car, Sayama.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:00.26,0:17:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Here?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.39,0:17:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you take her home?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:04.60,0:17:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.05,0:17:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful on your way home.
