Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.51,0:17:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you haven't grown at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:35.99,0:17:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:38.07,0:17:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to come after me, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:40.38,0:17:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, {\i1}someone's{\i0} self-absorbed.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.86,0:17:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I just came to find my old uniform \Nfrom during the Boatdrift Ceremony.{sic}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:47.87,0:17:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You two got in a fight, right?{nice rhyme}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:50.37,0:17:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls are always so quick to fight.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.68,0:17:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, they're quick to make up too.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:55.21,0:17:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beyond me.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.95,0:18:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure we'll be able \Nto make up this time...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:00.00,0:18:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you will.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.44,0:18:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know that!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.13,0:18:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka and Chisaki used to \Nfight all the time too, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:07.77,0:18:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san and Chisaki-san?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.36,0:18:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:11.38,0:18:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, Chisaki would stop talking to her.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Manaka would cry.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:17.23,0:18:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd they make up?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.40,0:18:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Who knows?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.26,0:18:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname probably used to help 'em out.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:27.23,0:18:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, guess I'll just have to play Kaname's role.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your nose! It looks like a red pig's!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.61,0:18:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.70,0:18:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, don't be mad.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.88,0:19:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Miu—
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.42,0:19:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:34.28,0:19:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's so cold.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:36.43,0:19:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:38.46,0:19:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It hurts.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:42.27,0:19:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hikari...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:51.49,0:19:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's that sound?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.93,0:19:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can breathe?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.69,0:20:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.17,0:20:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seeing Hikari underwater,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.19,0:20:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he shouldn't have looked \Nany different from usual.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.79,0:20:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet somehow, he seemed brighter... and extraordinary.{The New Shiny Hikari for a Special Price!}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.71,0:20:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:51.26,0:20:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was swimming!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:52.50,0:20:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wha—}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.40,0:20:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I could breathe!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:55.72,0:20:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea is so beautiful! It was amazing!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:03.53,0:21:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, quick!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:05.08,0:21:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:06.72,0:21:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go tell Mom I can swim!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:09.55,0:21:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't even difficult!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:14.81,0:21:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:17.03,0:21:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're okay...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:20.42,0:21:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I found this lying on the ground.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:23.94,0:21:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:26.37,0:21:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:27.81,0:21:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:32.06,0:21:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:34.73,0:21:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is a pig living in there or something?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:38.20,0:21:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How many you got in there?
